'''Matt Sloan''' is an Australian ex&ndash;special effects and animatronics technician who portrayed [[Plo Koon]] in [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']] and [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']]. He also worked as an animatronics technician in those films.

